#define gc getchar
int fastRead_int(){
    register int c=gc();
    int x=0, neg=0;
    for(; ((c<48 || c>57) && c != '-' && c!=EOF); c = gc());
    if(c==EOF) return EOF;
    if(c=='-')
    {
      neg = 1;
      c = gc();
    }
    for(; c>47 && c<58 ; c = gc()) {
      x = (x<<1) + (x<<3) + c - 48;
    }
    if(neg) x = -x;
    return x;
}
